RALLY CHAMPIONSHIPS:


        Find a car you want, but cant afford.  Now, leave the game.  Find
        the name of the car you want and .txt, so if you wanted an Escort,
        you would find Escort.txt.  Now use a text editor (I use TXED) and
        find a number (at the beginning).  It should look something like
        00000012345.  Now, replace the places where the 12345 # is and put
        0s in there place.  Now just leave a trailing 1.  Now the car will
        cost all of $10.  This is not only a way to get the car you want,
        but makes it cheaper to just buy a new car each time instead of
